http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#com.value: This vocabulary contains types of streets (thoroughfares) and street localities (street segments) as described by the Geocoded National Address File (GNAF). The vocabulary is derived from the GNAF's Street Type code list which is presented within the relational database versions of the GNAF as an authority table (lookup table). The values here are documented in the GNAF product guide. This vocabulary was originally created from the December, 2017, version of that guide.
